hadiths[108]{hadithnumber,text}:
2415,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum mein sey koi aisa nahin hai magar uska rab us sey qiyamat key roz kalam kerega aur dono key darmiyan koi tarjamaan nahin hoga, wo shakhs apney daain taraf dekhega to usey siwaye apney amal key koi chiz dikhai na deygi , phir baain janib dekhega to usey siwaye apney amal key koi chiz dikhai na deygi, phir samney dekhega to usey jahannam nazar aayegi.''  Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum mein sey jo jahannam ki garmi sey apney chehrey ko bachaanaa chahey to usey aisa karna chahiye, agar-che khajoor key eik tukdey hi key zariey kyon na ho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2416,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aadmi ka paaon qiyamat key din uskey rab key paas sey nahin hateyga yahan tak ke us sey paanch chizon key barey poochh liya jaey : uski umr key barey mein ke usey kahan kharch kiya, uski jawani key barey mein ke usey kahan khpaaya, uskey maal key barey mein ke usey kahan sey kamaya aur kis chiz mein kharch kiya aur uskey ilm key silsiley mein ke is par kahan tak amal kiya.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- isey hum « an ibne-Masood an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » ki sanad sey sirf Husain bin Qais hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain aur Husain bin Qais apney hifz key lihaaz sey zaeef hain. 2- is bab mein abu-Barza aur abu Saeed Khudri Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2417,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qiyamat key din kisi bandey key dono paaon nahin hateingey yahan tak ke us sey ye na poochh liya jaey : uski umr key barey mein ke usey kin kamon mein khatam kiya, aur uskey ilm key barey mein ke is par kya amal kiya aur uskey maal key barey mein ke usey kahan sey kamaya aur kahan kharch kiya, aur uskey jism key barey mein ke usey kahan khpaaya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Saeed bin Abdullah bin Juraij Basraa hain aur wo Abu-Barza key azad karda ghulam hain, Abu-Barza ka naam Nazlaa bin Ubaid hai."
2418,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney sawal kiya : ''kya tum logon ko malum hai ke muflis kisey kehtey hain?'' Sahaba ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! hamarey yahan muflis usey kehtey hain jis key paas dirham aur Dinar aur zaruri samane zindagi na ho, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''hamari ummat mein muflis wo shakhs hai jo qiyamat key din roza, namaz aur zakat key sath us haal mein aayega ke usney kisi ko gaali di hogi, kisi pe tohmat baandhi hogi, kisi ka maal khaya hoga, kisi ka khoon bahaayaa hoga, aur kisi ko maara hoga, phir usey sab key samney bithaya jaeyga aur badley mein uski nekiyan mazlumon ko dey di jaeyngi, phir agar uskey zulmon ka badla pura honey sey pehley uski nekiyan khatam ho jaeyngi to mazlumon key gunah ley kar is par rakh diye jaeyngey aur usey jahannam mein dal diya jaeyga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2419,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah taala aisey bandey par reham karey jis key paas uskey bhai ki izzat ya maal mein koi badla ho, phir wo marney sey pehley hi uskey paas aa key duniya hi mein us sey maaf kara ley kyonkey qiyamat key roz na to uskey paas Dinar hoga aur na hi dirham , phir agar zalim key paas kuchh nekiyan hongi to uski nekiyon sey badla liya jaeyga aur agar uskey paas nekiyan bhi nahin hongi to mazlumon key gunah zalim key sar par dal diye jaeyngey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Saeed Maqbari ki riwayat sey Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- Malik bin Anas ney « an Saeed Al Maqbari an Abi Huraira an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » ki sanad sey isi jaisi hadees riwayat ki hai."
2420,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''(qiyamat key din) haqdaaron ko unka pura pura haq diya jaeyga, yahan tak ke seeng wali bakri sey baghair seeng wali bakri ka badla liya jaeyga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Zar aur Abdullah bin Unais Raziallahu anhuma sey ahadees aai hain."
2421,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko ye farmatey huye suna : ''qiyamat key din suraj ko bandon sey qarib kar diya jaeyga, yahan tak ke wo un sey eik meel ya do meel key fasley par hoga.'' Raavi Sulaim bin Aamir kehtey hain : mujhey nahin malum ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney kon si meel murad li hai.  (zameen ki masafat ya aankh mein surma laganey ki salaai) ''phir suraj unhen pighla dega aur log apney aamal key aetbar sey paseeney mein doobey hongey, baaz ediyon tak , baaz ghutney tak , baaz kamar tak aur baaz ka paseena munh tak lagaam ki maanind hoga.'' miqdaad (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai : mainey dekha ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam apney haath sey apney munh ki taraf ishara kar rahey hain ke paseena logon key munh tak pahunch jaeyga jaisey ke lagaam lagi hoti hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein abu Saeed Khudri aur Abdullah bin umr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2422,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney is aayate-karima ki tilawat farmaee : « يوم يقوم الناس لرب العالمين » ''jis din log Rabbul Aalameen key samney khadey hongey'' (Sura Mutaffefeen : 6), aur kaha : ''us din log Allah key samney us haal mein khadey hongey ke paseena unkey aadhey kanon tak hoga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2423,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qiyamat key din logon ka hashr us haal mein hoga ke wo nangey badan, nangey pair aur khatna key baghair hongey , phir aap ney is aayate-karima ki tilawat ki : (كما بدأنا أول خلق نعيده وعدا علينا إنا كنا فاعلين) ''jaisey ke hamney awwal dafa paidaish ki thi isi tarah dobara karengey, ye hamarey zimmey wada hai, aur hum isey zarur kar key hi rahengey.'' (Sura Anmbiya : 104), insanon mein sab sey pehley Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ko kapda pehnaya jaeyga, aur meri ummat key baaz log daain aur baain taraf ley jaey jaeyngey to main kahunga : merey Rab ! ye to merey ummati hain, to kaha jaeyga aap ko nahin malum ke un logon ney aap key baad Deen mein kya naee naee baaten nikalin, aur jab sey aap un sey juda huye ho ye log hamesha Deen sey phirtey rahey hain, to us waqt main wohi kahunga jo (Allah key) nek bandey Esa (Alaihissalam) ney kahi thi : « إن تعذبهم فإنهم عبادك وإن تغفر لهم فإنك أنت العزيز الحكيم » ''agar to unhen azab dey to yaqinan ye terey bandey hain aur agar unhen to bakhsh dey to yaqinan to ghalib aur hikmat wala hai.'' (Al-Maeyda : 118)."
2424,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko ye farmatey huye suna : ''tum log maidane-hashr mein pedal aur sawar laye jaaogey aur apney chehron key bal ghasitey jaaogey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2425,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qiyamat key din logon ki teen peshiyan hongi, do baar ki peshi mein behes aur takraar aur uzr aur bahaney hongey , aur teesri baar un logon key aamal namey unkey haathon mein oud rahey hongey, to koi usey apney dahiney haath mein pakdey hoga aur koi baaein hath mein.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih nahin hai, isliye ke Hasan ka samaa (sun'na), Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey Sabit nahin hai. 2- baaz logon ney is hadees ko : (عن علي الرفاعي an الحسن an أبي موسى an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) ki sanad sey riwayat kiya hai. 3- ye hadees bhi sahih nahin hai kyonkey Hasan ka samaa (sun'na), abu-Musa Ash-ari sey bhi Sabit nahin hai."
2426,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna ke jis sey hisab aur kitab mein sakhti sey poochh taachh ho gaee wo halak ho jaeyga. mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! Allah Taala farmata hai :« فأما man أوتي كتابه بيمينه فسوف يحاسب حسابا يسيرا » ''jis shakhs ko namae-aemal uskey daain haath mein diya jaeyga to us sey aasan hisab liya jaeyga.'' (Al Inshiqaaq : 7). aap ney farmaya : ''is sey murad sirf aamal ki peshi hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih Hasan hai. 2- Ayub ney bhi ibne-Abi Muleka sey is hadees ki riwayat ki hai.
2427,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''ibne-Adam ko qiyamat key roz bhaid key bachchey ki shakal mein Allah Taala key huzur pesh kiya jaeyga, Allah Taala us sey puchheyga : mainey tujhey maal aur asbab sey nawaza, aur tujh par inaam kiya usmein tuney kya amal kiya? wo kaheyga aey merey Rab ! mainey bahut sara maal jama kiya aur isey badhaya aur duniya mein usey pehley sey ziyada hi chhod kar aaya , so mujhey duniya mein dobara bhej ! taake main un sab ko ley aaun , Allah Taala farmaeyga , jo kuchh tu ney amale-khair kiya hai isey dikha , wo kaheyga : aey merey rab ! mainey bahut sara maal jama kiya, usey badhaya aur duniya mein pehley sey ziyada hi chhod kar aaya , mujhey dobara bhej taake main usey ley aaun , ye us bandey ka haal hoga jisney khair aur bhalai ki raah mein koi maal kharch nahin kiya hoga, chunanche usey Allah key hukm key mutabiq jahannam mein dal diya jaeyga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ki riwayat kaee logon ney Hasan Basri sey ki hai, aur kaha hai ke ye unka qol hai, usey marfoo nahin kiya. 2- Ismail bin Muslim Zaeef hain, unkey hifz key talluq sey kalam kiya gaya hai. 3- is bab mein Abu-Hurera aur abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2428,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qiyamat key din eik bandey ko laya jaeyga, Bari Taala us sey farmaeyga : kya mainey tujhey kaan , aankh maal aur aulad sey nahin nawaza tha? aur chopayon aur kheti ko terey tabey kar diya tha, aur qom ka tujhey sardar bana diya tha jin sey bharpur khidmat liya karta tha, phir kya tujhey ye khayal bhi tha ke to aaj key din mujh sey mulaqat kerega? wo arz kerega : nahin, Allah Taala farmaeyga : aaj main bhi tujhey bhool jata hun jaisey to mujhey duniya mein bhool gaya tha.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih gharib hai. 2- Allah Taala key farman : « اليوم أنساك » ka matlab ye hai ke aaj key din main tujhey azab mein wesay hi chhod dunga jaisey bhooli chiz padi rehti hai. baaz ehle-ilm ney isi tarah sey uski tafseer ki hai. 3- baaz ehle-ilm aayate-karima « فاليوم ننساهم » ki ye tafseer ki hai ke aaj key din hum tumhen azab mein bhooli hui chiz ki tarah chhod dengey."
2429,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aayate-karima : « يومئذ تحدث أخبارها » ki tilawat ki aur farmaya : ''kya tum logon ko malum hai ke iski khabren kya hongi?'' Sahaba ney arz kiya : Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain, aap ney farmaya : ''uski khabren ye hain ke wo har mard aur aurat key khilaf gawahi deygi, jo kaam bhi unhoney zamin par kiya hoga, wo kaheygi ke usney falan falan din aisa aisa kaam kiya.''  aap ney farmaya : ''yehi uski khabren hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
2430,"eik Erabi (dehati) (dehati) ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki khidmat mein aa kar arz kiya : «soor» kya chiz hai? aap ney farmaya : ''eik sankh hai jis mein phunk maari jaeygi.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- kaee logon ney Suleman (Alaihissalam) Taimi sey is hadees ki riwayat ki hai, isey hum sirf Suleman (Alaihissalam) Taimi ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
2431,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main kaisey aaram karun jabke soor waley Israafeel (Alaihissalam) « soor » ko munh mein liye huye us hukm par kaan lagaey huye hain ke kab phoonkney ka hukm sadir (jaari) ho aur is mein phunk maari jaey, goya ye Amr Sahaba kiram (Raziallauh anhum) par sakht guzri, to aap ney farmaya : kaho : (حسبنا الله ونعم الوكيل على الله توكلنا) yani ''Allah hamarey liye kafi hai kya hi achchha kaar-saaz hai wo Allah hi par hamney tawakkul kiya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- ye hadees Atiya sey kaee sanadon sey abu Saeed Khudri key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
2432,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''pul-siraat par momin ka shiaar ye hoga : (رب سلم سلم) merey rab ! mujhey salaamat rakh , mujhey salaamat rakh.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Mughira bin Shoba ki riwayat sey gharib hai, isey hum sirf Abdur-Rehman bin Is-haq (Waasti hi) ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai."
2433,"mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey darkhaast ki ke aap qiyamat key din merey liye shafaat farmaeyn, aap ney farmaya : ''zarur karunga'' mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! main aap ko kahan talash karunga? aap ney farmaya : ''sab sey pehley mujhey pul-siraat par dhundna.''  mainey arz kiya : agar pul-siraat par aap sey mulaqat na ho sakey, to farmaya : ''to uskey baad meezaan (taraazu) key paas dhundna.''  mainey kaha : agar meezaan key paas bhi mulaqat na ho sakey to? farmaya : ''uskey baad hoze kausar par dhundna isliye ke main in teen jagahon mein sey kisi jagah par zarur miloonga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. isey hum sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
2434,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki khidmat mein gosht pesh kiya gaya, is mein sey aap ko dast ka gosht diya gaya jo ke aap ko bahut pasand tha, isey aap ney noch noch kar khaya , phir farmaya : ''qiyamat key din main logon ka sardar rahunga , kya tum logon ko iski wajeh malum hai? wo isliye ke us din Allah Taala eik humwaar kushada zamin par agley pichley tamam logon ko jama kerega, jinhen eik pukarney wala aawaz dega aur unhen har nigah wala dekh sakeyga, suraj un sey bilkul qarib hoga jis sey logon ka gham auraichaini is qadr badh jaeygi jiski na wo taqat rakhengey aur na hi usey bardasht kar sakengey, log eik doosrey sey kahengey : kya nahin dekhtey ke tumhari musibat kahan tak pahunch gaee hai, aisey shakhs ko kyon nahin dekhtey jo tumharey rab sey tumharey liye shafaat kerey. to baaz log baaz sey kahengey ki Adam (Alaihissalam) key paas chalen , lihaza log Adam (Alaihissalam) key paas aa kar arz kerengey ke aap Abul Bishr hain, Allah Taala ney aap ko apney haath sey paida kiya, aap key andar apni rooh phunki , farishton ko hukm diya jinhoney aap ko sajda kiya, lihaza aap hamarey liye apney rab sey shafaat kar dijiye. kya aap hamari haalate zaar ko nahin dekh rahey hain ke hamein kitni musibat laahiq hai? Adam (Alaihissalam) un sey kahengey ki aaj mera rab aisa ghazabnaak hai ke is sey pehley na to aisa ghussa huwa aur na kabhi aisa ghussa hoga, yaqinan usney mujhey eik darkht sey mana farmaya tha, lekin mainey uski nafarmani ki, aaj meri zaat ka maamla hai, nafsaa nafsi ka aalim hai, tum log kisi aur key paas jaao , Nuh key paas jaao , chunanche wo log Nuh (Alaihissalam) key paas aa kar arz kerengey, aey Nuh ! aap zamin walon ki taraf bhejey gaey, pehley Rasool they, Allah ney aap ko shukar-guzar banda kaha hai, lihaza aap hamarey liye apney rab sey shafaat kar dijiye , kya aap hamari haalate zaar ko nahin dekh rahey hain ke hamein kitni musibat laahiq hai, Nuh (Alaihissalam) un logon sey farmaeyngey ke aaj mera rab aisa ghazabnaak hai ke na to is sey pehley aisa ghussa huwa aur na kabhi aisa ghussa hoga, merey liye eik maqbool dua thi jisey mainey apni qom ki halakat key liye istimal kar liya, aur aaj meri zaat ka maamla hai, nafsi nafsi nafsi, tum log kisi aur key paas jaao, Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) key paas jaao , chunanche wo log Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) key paas aa kar arz kerengey : aey Ibrahim ! aap zamin walon mein sey Allah key Nabi aur uskey khaleel (yani gehrey dost) hain, lihaza aap hamarey liye apney rab sey shafaat kar dijiye, kya aap hamari haalate-zaar ko nahin dekh rahey hain? wo farmaeyngey ke aaj key din mera rab itna ghazabnaak hai ke is sey pehley na to aisa ghussa huwa aur na kabhi aisa ghussa hoga, aur main duniya key andar teen jhoot bol chuka hun (abu-Hayyaan ney apni riwayat mein un teeno jhoot ka zikr kiya hai) aaj meri zaat ka maamla hai, nafsi nafsi nafsi, tum log kisi aur key paas jaao , Musa key paas jaao , chunanche wo log Musa (Alaihissalam) key paas aa kar arz karengey ke aey Musa ! aap Allah key Rasool hain, Allah ney aap ko apni risalat aur apney kalam key zariey tamam logon par fazilat ata ki hai, lihaza aap hamarey liye apney rab sey shafaat kar dijiye, kya aap hamari haalate zaar ko nahin dekh rahey hain? wo farmaeyngey ke aaj key din mera rab itna ghazabnaak hai ke is sey pehley na to aisa ghussa huwa aur na kabhi aisa ghussa hoga, duniya key andar mainey eik shakhs ko maar dala tha jisey maarney ka mujhey hukm nahin diya gaya tha, aaj mujhey apni jaan ki fikr hai, nafsi nafsi nafsi, tum log kisi aur key paas jaao, Esa key paas jaao, chunanche wo log Esa (Alaihissalam) key paas aa kar arz kerengey : aey Esa ! aap Allah key Rasool , aur uska kalma hain jisey usney Maryam  ki taraf dala aap Allah ki rooh hain, aap ney logon sey god hi mein kalam kiya, lihaza aap hamarey liye apney rab sey shafaat kar dijiye, kya aap hamari haalat zaar ko nahin dekh rahey hain. Esa (Alaihissalam) farmaeyngey : aaj key din mera rab itna ghazabnaak hai ke is sey pehley na to aisa ghussa huwa aur na kabhi aisa ghussa hoga, aur unhoney apni kisi ghalati ka zikr nahin kiya aur kaha ke aaj to meri zaat ka maamla hai, nafsi nafsi nafsi, tum log kisi aur key paas jaao, Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas jaao, Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : chunanche wo log Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar arz kerengey : aey Muhammad ! aap Allah key Rasool aur uskey aakhiri Nabi hain, aap key agley aur pichhley tamam gunah maaf kar diye gaey hain, lihaza aap hamarey liye apney rab sey shafaat kijiye , kya aap hamari haalate zaar ko nahin dekh rahey hain, (aagey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam farmatey hain) ''phir main chal padoonga aur arsh key nichey aa kar apney rab ki tazeem key liye sajdey mein gir jaaunga, phir Allah Taala merey ooper apney Mahamid aur  khoobiyon ko is qadr khol dega ke mujh sey pehley itna kisi par nahin khola hoga, phir mujh sey kaha jaeyga ke aey Muhammad ! apney sar ko uthaao aur sawal karo, usey pura kiya jaeyga, aur shafaat karo, tumhari shafaat qubul ki jaeygi, chunanche main apna sar uthaaunga aur kahunga : aey merey rab ! main apni ummat ki najat aur falah (kaamiyaabi) maangta hun, aey merey rab main apni ummat ki najat aur falah (kaamiyaabi) maangta hun, aey merey rab ! main apni ummat ki najat aur falah (kaamiyaabi) maangta hun, Allah Taala farmaeyga : aey Muhammad ! apni ummat mein sey un logon ko jannat key darwazon mein sey dahiney darwazey sey dakhil kar lein, jin par koi hisab aur kitab nahin hai, aur ye sab (ummate Muhammad) deegar darwazon mein bhi (dakhil honey mein) aur logon key sath shareek hongey.''  phir aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qasam hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! jannat key paton mein sey do pat key darmiyan ka fasla itna hi hai jitna ke Makka aur Hijr ya Makka aur Basraa key darmiyan fasla hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein abu-Bakar Siddiq , Anas , Aqba bin Aamir aur abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallauh anhum) sey ahadees aai hain."
2435,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''meri shafaat meri ummat key kabeera gunah walon key liye hogi.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2436,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''meri shafaat meri ummat key kabeera gunah walon key liye hogi.'' Muhammad bin Ali Baaqar kehtey hain : mujh sey Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Muhammad ! jo bade gunaaho mein sey na hongey unhen shafaat sey kya talluq? Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Jaafar Sadiq bin Muhammad Al Baaqar ki riwayat sey Hasan gharib hai.
2437,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : ''merey rab ney mujh sey wada farmaya hai ke wo meri ummat mein sey sattar hazar logon ko jannat mein dakhil karega, na unka hisab hoga aur na un par koi azab, (phir) har hazar key sath sattar hazar hongey, aur unkey siwa merey rab ki muththiyon mein sey teen muththiyon key barabar bhi hongey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
2438,"main Eiliyaa main eik jamaat key sath tha, un mein sey eik aadmi ney kaha ke mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna hai : ''meri ummat key eik fard ki shafaat sey qabila bani Tameem ki tadaad sey bhi ziyada log jannat mein dakhil hongey.'' kisi ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! kya wo shakhs aap key ilawa hoga? aap ney farmaya : ''haan, merey ilawa hoga''  phir jab wo (Raavi hadees) khadey huye to mainey puchha : ye kon hain? logon ney kaha ye ibne-Abi Jazaa (Raziallahu anhu) hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- ibne-Abi Jazaa (Raziallahu anhu) ka naam Abdullah hai, un sey sirf yehi eik hadees mash'hoor hai."
2439,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) qiyamat key din qabila Rabeea aur Muzir key barabar, logon key liye shafaat karengey.''"
2440,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''meri ummat ka koi shakhs kaee jamaat key liye shafaat kerega, koi eik qabeele key liye shafaat karega, koi eik giroh key liye shafaat kerega, aur koi eik aadmi key liye shafaat kerega, yahan tak ke sab jannat mein dakhil hun jaeyngey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
2441,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''merey rab ki taraf sey eik aaney wala (Jibreel (Alaihissalam)) merey paas aaya aur mujhey ikhtiyar diya ke meri aadhi ummat jannat mein dakhil ho ya ye ke mujhey shafaat ka haq hasil ho, chunanche mainey shafaat ko ikhtiyar kiya, ye shafaat har us shakhs key liye hai jiska khatima shirk ki haalat par nahin hoga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees abu-Mulaih ney eik aur Sabab sey riwayat ki hai aur unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai, (lekin) is mein Auf bin Malik ka zikr nahin kiya, is hadees main eik taweel qissa mazkur hai."
2442,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''beshak merey hoz par aasman key taaron ki tadaad key barabar piyaley hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai.
2443,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qiyamat key roz har Nabi key liye eik hoz hoga, aur wo aapas main eik doosrey par fakhr kerengey ke kis key hoz par pani peeney waley ziyada jama hotey hain, aur mujhey ummid hai ke merey hoz par) Allah key Fazal sey) sab sey ziyada log jama hongey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- Ash-as bin abdul-Malik ney is hadees ko Hasan Basri key wastey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursalan riwayat kiya hai aur is mein Samura ka zikr nahin kiya hai, ye riwayat ziyada sahih hai."
2444,"umr bin Abdul-Azeez ney merey paas bulaawey ka pegham bheja , chunanche main daak-sawari khachchar par sawar ho kar aap key paas pahuncha , mainey kaha : aey Ameerul-momineen daak sawari khachchar ki sawari mujh par shaaq guzri to unhoney kaha : abu Salam ! main tumhen takleef dena nahin chahta tha, lekin mainey tumharey barey mein ye suna hai ke tum Soban (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey hoze kausar key barey main eik hadees riwayat kartey ho, chunanche meri ye khahish hui ke wo hadees tum sey baraahe-raast sun lun, abu Salam ney kaha : Soban (Raziallahu anhu) ney mujh sey bayan kiya ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''mera hoz itna bada hai jitna adn sey urdan waley ammaan tak ka fasla hai, uska pani doodh sey ziyada safed aur shehad sey ziyada mitha hai, uskey piyaley aasman key taaron ki tadaad key barabar hain, us sey jo eik martaba pi leyga kabhi piyasa na hoga, sab sey pehley is par fuqaraa muhajrin pahuncheingey, jinkey sar dhool sey atey hongey aur unkey kapdey mailey kuchele hongey, jo naaz aur nakhre wali aurton sey nikah nahin kar saktey aur na unkey liye auhade aur manzilat key darwazey nahi kholey jatey.'' umr bin abdul-Azeez ney kaha : lekin mainey to naaz aur nakhron mein palee aurton sey nikah kiya aur merey liye auhde aur manzilat key darwazey bhi kholey gaey, mainey Fatima binte abdul-Malik sey nikah kiya, albatta itni baat zarur hai ke apney sar ko nahin dhota yahan tak ke wo ghubar aalud na ho jaey aur apney badan key kapdey us waqt tak nahin dhota jab tak ke mailey na ho jaeyn. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai. 2- ye hadees Maadaan bin Abi Talha key wastey sey « an Soban an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » ki sanad sey bhi marvi hai. 3- abu Salam Habshi ka naam Mamtoor hai, ye Shaami hain aur Suqa (bharosemand) Raavi hain."
2445,"mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! hoze kausar key bartan kaisey hain? aap ney farmaya : '' qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! yaqinan uskey bartan taaron sey bhi ziyada hain us taareek (andheri) raat mein jis mein aasman sey badal chhat gaya ho, aur uskey piyaley jannat key bartanon mein sey hongey , us sey jo eik martaba pi leyga wo kabhi piyasa na hoga, uski chorai uski lambaai key barabar hai, uska fasla itna hai jitna ammaan sey Eila tak ka fasla hai. uska pani doodh sey ziyada safed aur shehad sey ziyada mitha hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Huzefa bin Yamaan, Abdullah bin Amr , abu-Barza Aslami , ibne-Umar , Harisa bin Wahab aur Mustaurid bin Shaddad (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''merey hoz ka fasla itna hai jitna koofa sey Hajare Aswad tak ka fasla hai.''"
2446,"jab Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Meraj key liye tashrif ley gaey to wahan aap ka eik Nabi aur kaee nabiyon key paas sey guzar huwa, un mein sey kisi Nabi key sath un ki puri ummat thi, kisi key sath eik jamaat thi, kisi key sath koi na tha, yahan tak ke aap ka guzar eik badey giroh sey huwa , to aap ney puchha ye kon hain? kaha gaya : ye Musa aur un ki qom hai, aap apney sar ko buland kijiye aur dekhiye : to yakayak mainey eik bahut bada giroh dekha jisney aasman key kinaron ko us janib sey us janib tak gher rakha tha, mujh sey kaha gaya ke ye aap ki ummat hai aur iskey siwa aap ki ummat mein sattar hazar aur hain jo jannat mein baghair hisab key dakhil hongey, phir aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ghar mein tashrif ley gaey aur log aap sey uski baabat nahin poochh sakey aur na hi aap ney unkey samney uski tafseer bayan ki, chunanche un mein sey baaz Sahaba ney kaha : shayad wo hum hi log hon aur baaz ney kaha : shayad hamari wo aulad hain jo fitrate Islam par paida huin. log guftgu kar hi rahey they ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam bahar nikal aaye aur farmaya : ''ye wo log hongey jo na badan par dagh lagwaate hain aur na jhaad phunk aur mantar karwaatey hain aur na hi bad-shaguni letey hain, wo sirf apney rab par tawakkul aur aitimad kartey hain.'' isi asnaa mein Ukaasha bin Mohsin (Raziallahu anhu) ney khadey ho kar arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! kya main bhi unhi mein sey hun? aap ney farmaya : ''haan'' (tum bhi unhi mein sey ho) phir eik doosrey shakhs ney khadey ho kar arz kiya : kya main bhi unhi mein sey hun? to aap ney farmaya : ''Ukaasha ney tum par sabqat hasil kar li.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.  2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera aur ibne-Masood Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2447,"main wo cheezen nahin dekhta jin par hum Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zamaney mein amal kartey they, Raavi hadees abu-Imraan Jawni ney kaha : kya aap namaz nahin dekhtey? Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : kya tum logon ney namaz mein wo sab nahin kiya jo tum jantey ho?  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees abu-Imraan Jawni ki riwayat sey gharib Hasan hai. 2- ye hadees Anas key wastey sey iskey ilawa aur kaee sanadon sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
2448,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko ye farmatey huye suna : ''bura hai wo banda jo takabbur karey aur itraaey aur Allah buzurg aur bartar ko bhool jaey, aur bura hai wo banda jo mazlumon par qehar dhaey aur zulm aur ziyadti karey aur Allah jabbaar bartar ko bhool jaey, aur bura hai wo banda jo khail aur tamashon mein mashghool ho aur qabron aur haddiyon key sadh gal janey ko bhool jaey, aur bura hai wo banda jo had sey aagey badh jaey aur sarkashi ka raasta apnaey aur apni paidaish aur maut ko bhool jaey, aur bura hai wo banda jo Deen key badley duniya ko talab karey , aur bura hai wo banda jo apney Deen ko shub'haat sey milaaey , aur bura hai wo banda jisey lalach apni taraf khinch ley , aur bura hai wo banda jisey uska nafs hi gumrah kar dey aur bura hai wo banda jisey hirs zaleel aur ruswa kar dey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai, isey hum sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain aur iski sanad qawi nahin hai."
2449,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo momin banda kisi bhookey momin ko khana khilaaeyga usey Allah Taala qiyamat key roz jannat key phal khilaaeyga, aur jo momin banda kisi piyasey momin ko pani palaeyga, qiyamat key roz Allah Taala usey «الرحيق المختوم» (mohar band sharab) palaeyga, aur jo momin banda kisi nangey badan waley momin ko kapda pahnaaeyga Allah Taala usey jannat key sabz (hara) jodey pahnaaeyga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- ye hadees Atiya key wastey sey abu Saeed Khudri sey mauqufan marvi hai, aur hamarey nazdik yehi sanad sab sey ziyada qareeb aur sahih hai."
2450,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo dushman key hamle sey dara aur shuru raat hi mein safar mein nikal pada wo manzil ko pahunch gaya padhi. , aagah raho ! Allah Taala ka saman badi qeemat wala hai, aagah raho ! Allah Taala ka saman jannat hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan , gharib hai, isey hum sirf abu-Nazar hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
2451,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''banda muttaqiyon key maqam ko nahin pahunch sakta jab tak ke wo is baat ko jis mein koi harj na ho, us chiz sey bachney key liye na chhod dey, jis mein burai hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, isey hum sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
2452,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''agar tumhari wohi keyfiyat rahey , jaisi merey samney hoti hai to farishtey apney paron sey tum par saya karen.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- ye hadees Hanzala Usedi key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey is sanad key ilawa deegar sanadon sey bhi marvi hai. 3- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat aai hai."
2453,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''har chiz ki eik hirs aur khushi hoti hai, aur har hirs aur khushi ki eik kamzori hoti hai, to agar uska apnaney wala moatadil munasib raftaar chala aur haq key qarib hota raha to uski behtari ki ummid rakho , aur agar uski taraf ungliyon sey ishara kiya jaaey to usey kuchh shumar mein na laao.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai. Anas bin Malik sey riwayat hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aadmi key bigaad key liye itna hi kafi hai ke uskey Deen ya duniya key barey mein uski taraf ungliyan uthai jaeyn , magar jisey Allah Taala mehfooz rakhey.''"
2454,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik Mirbbaa khat (yani chaukor) lakeer khinchi aur eik lakeer darmiyan mein us sey bahar nikalte huwe khinchi, aur us darmiyani lakeer key baghal mein chand chhoti chhoti lakeerein aur khinchi , phir farmaya : ''ye ibne-Adam hai aur ye lakeer uski maut ki hai jo har taraf sey usey gherey huye hai. aur ye darmiyan wali lakeer insan hai (yani uski aarzuein hain) aur ye chhoti chhoti lakeerein insan ko pesh aaney waley haadisen hain, agar eik haadise sey wo bach nikla to doosra usey das leyga aur bahar nikalney wala khat uski ummid hai."
2455,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aadmi boodha ho jata hai lekin uski do khawhishen jawan rehti hain : eik maal ki hawas dusri lambi umr ki tamanna.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2456,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aadmi ki misal aisi hai ke uskey pehlu mein ninnanwey aafaten hain, agar wo un aafaton sey bach gaya to budhapey mein giraftar ho jaeyga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
2457,"jab do tihai raat guzar jati to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam uthtey aur farmatey : logo ! Allah ko yad karo, Allah ko yad karo, khad-khadaane wali aa gaee hai aur uskey sath eik dusri aa lagi hai, maut apni fauj ley kar aa gaee hai. maut apni fauj ley kar aa gaee hai.''  mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! main aap par bahut salaat ( durood ( padha karta hun to apney wazeefey mein aap par durood padhney key liye kitna waqt muqarrar kar lun? aap ney farmaya : ''jitna tum chaho''  mainey arz kiya chothai? aap ney farmaya : ''jitna tum chaho aur agar is sey ziyada kar lo to tumharey haq mein behtar hai.''  mainey arz kiya : aadha? aap ney farmaya : ''jitna tum chaho aur agar is sey ziyada kar lo to tumharey haq mein behtar hai, mainey arz kiya do tihai?'' aap ney farmaya : ''jitna tum chaho aur agar is sey ziyada kar lo to tumharey haq mein behtar hai, mainey arz kiya : wazeefey mein pura waqt aap par durood padha karun?  aap ney farmaya : ''ab ye durood tumharey sab ghamon key liye kafi hoga aur is sey tumharey gunah bakhsh diye jaaeyngey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2458,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah taala sey sharam aur hayaa karo jaisa ke us sey sharam aur hayaa karney ka haq hai.'' padhi. ,hum ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! hum Allah sey sharam aur hayaa kartey hain aur is par Allah ka shukar ada kartey hain, aap ney farmaya : ''hayaa ka ye haq nahin jo tum ney samjha hai, Allah sey sharam aur hayaa karney ka jo haq hai wo ye hai ke tum apney sar aur uskey sath jitni cheezen hain un sab ki hifazat karo, aur apney pet aur uskey andar jo cheezen hain un ki hifazat karo padhi. , aur maut aur haddiyon key gal sad janey ko yad kiya karo, aur jisey aakhirat ki chaahat ho wo duniya ki zeb aur zeenat ko tarak kar dey isliye jisney ye sab pura kiya to haqiqat mein usi ney Allah Taala sey hayaa ki jaisa ke us sey hayaa karney ka haq hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- is hadees ko is sanad sey hum sirf Aban bin Is-haq ki riwayat sey jantey hain, aur unhoney Sabaah bin Muhammad sey riwayat ki hai."
2459,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aqlmand wo hai jo apney nafs ko raam kar ley aur maut key baad ki zindagi key liye amal karey aur aajiz aur bewaquf wo hai jo apney nafs ko khaahishat par laga dey aur rehmate Ilaahi ki aarzu rakhey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- aur (من دان نفسه) ka matlab ye hai ke wo duniya hi mein apney nafs ka muhaasba (jaaiyza) kar ley is sey pehley ke qiyamat key roz uska muhaasba kiya jaey. 3- umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : apney nafs ka muhaasba karo qabl uskey ke tumhara muhaasba kiya jaey, aur  (aakhirat ki peshi) key liye tadbeer karo, aur jo shakhs duniya hi mein apney nafs ka muhaasba karta hai qiyamat key roz is par hisab aur kitab aasan hoga. 4- Memun bin Mehran kehtey hain : banda muttaqi aur perhezgar nahin hota yahan tak ke wo apney nafs ka muhaasba karey jaisa ke apney shareek sey muhaasba karta hai aur ye khayal karey ke mera khana aur libas kahan sey hai."
2460,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam apney musalley par tashrif laye aur dekha ke log hans rahey hain, aap ney farmaya : ''aagah raho ! agar tum log lazzaton ko khatam kar deney wali chiz ko yad rakhtey to tum apni un harkaton sey baaz rehtey, to lazzaton ko khatam kar deney wali maut ka zikr kasrat sey karo, isliye ke qabr rozaana bolti hai aur kehti hai : main ghurbat ka ghar hun, main tanhai ka ghar hun, main mitti ka ghar hun, aur main keedey makodon ka ghar hun, phir jab momin bandey ko dafn kiya jata hai to qabr usey marhabaa ( khush aamadeed ( kehti hai aur Mubarak baad deti hai aur kehti hai : beshak to merey nazdik un mein sab sey ziyada mehbub tha jo merey peeth par chaltey hain, phir ab jabke main terey kaam ki nigran ho gaee aur to meri taraf aa gaya to ab dekh leyga ke main terey sath kaisa husne-suluk karungi, phir uski nazar pahunchney tak qabr kushada kar di jaeygi aur uskey liye jannat ka eik darwaza khol diya jaeyga, aur jab faajir ya kafir dafn kiya jata hai to qabr usey na hi marhabaa kehti hai aur na hi Mubarak baad deti hai balke kehti hai : beshak to merey nazdik un mein sab sey ziyada qabile nafrat tha jo meri peeth par chaltey hain, phir ab jabke main terey kaam ki nigran hun aur to meri taraf aa gaya to aaj to apney sath meri badsulukiyan dekh leyga, phir wo usko dabaati hai, aur har taraf sey is par zor daalti hai yahan tak ke uski pasliyan eik taraf sey dusri taraf mil jati hain, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apni ungliyon sey ishara kiya aur eik doosrey ko aapas mein dakhil kar key farmaya : ''Allah is par sattar azdahe muqarrar kar dega, agar un mein sey koi eik baar bhi zamin par phunk maar dey to is par rehti duniya tak kabhi ghaas na ugey, phir wo azdahe usey hisab aur kitab liye janey tak daanton sey kaateingey aur nochengey.'' ,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''beshak qabr jannat key baaghon mein sey eik baagh hai ya jahannam key ghadon mein sey eik gadha hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, isey hum sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
2461,"main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki khidmat mein hazir huwa us haal mein ke aap chataai par tek lagaey huye they to mainey dekha ke chataai ka nishan aap key pehlu par asar kar gaye hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is hadees main eik taweel qissa hai, (wohi aap ka azwaje-mutahrat (paak biwiyon) sey elaa karney ka qissa hai)."
2462,"Amr bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) (ye banu Aamir bin Luai key haleef aur jange-badar mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath hazir they) ney mujhey khabar di ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah (Raziallahu anhu) ko bheja phir wo Behrein (Aehsa) sey kuchh maale-ghanimat ley kar aaye , jab ansaar ney abu-Ubaida key aaney ki khabar suni to wo sab Fajr mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath shareek huye, udhar jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam namaze Fajr sey farigh ho kar wapis huye to log aap key samney aaye. jab aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sab ko dekha to muskuraaey aur farmaya : ''shayad tum logon ney ye baat sun li hai ke abu-Ubaida kuchh ley kar aaye hain.'' , logon ney kaha ji haan , Allah key Rasool ! aap ney farmaya : ''tumharey liye khushkhabri hai aur us chiz ki ummid rakho jo tumhen khush karey , Allah ki qism ! main tum par faqr (ghurbat) aur mohtaji sey nahin darta hun, albatta mujhey ye andesha hai ke duniya tum par kushada kar di jaey, jaisa ke tum sey pehley logon par kushada ki gaee , phir tum is mein hirs aur raghbat karney lago jaisa ke un logon ney hirs aur raghbat ki, phir duniya tumhen tabah aur barbad kar dey jaisa ke usney unko tabah aur barbad kiya.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2463,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey manga to aap ney mujhey diya, phir manga to phir diya, phir manga to phir diya, phir aap ney farmaya : ''Hakeem ! beshak ye maal hara bhara mitha hai, jo isey khush dili sey ley leyga to usey is mein barkat nasib hogi, aur jo isey laalchi bankar leyga usey is mein barkat hasil na hogi , aur uski misal aisey hi hai jo khata hai lekin aasooda (mutmaeen) nahin hota, aur ooper ka haath ( deney wala ( nichey key haath ( leney waley ( sey behtar hai.'' ,Hakeem kehtey hain : mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! qism hai us zaat ki jisney aap ko haq key sath bheja hai ! aap key baad main kisi sey kuch na lunga yahan tak ke duniya sey rukhsat ho jaaun, phir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu), Hakeem (Raziallahu anhu) ko kuchh deney key liye bulatey to wo usey qubul karney sey inkar kar detey , unkey baad umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney bhi unhen kuchh deney key liye bulaya to usey bhi qubul karney sey inkar kar diya, chunanche umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : aey musalmanon ki jamaat ! main tum logon ko Hakeem par gawah banata hun ke is maale ghanimat mein sey main unka haq pesh karta hun to wo isey leney sey inkar kartey hain, chunanche Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key baad Hakeem (Raziallahu anhu) ney kisi shakhs key maal sey kuchh nahin liya yahan tak ke wo duniya sey rukhsat ho gaey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai."
2464,"hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath takleef aur tangi mein aazamaye gaey to is par hamney sabr kiya, phir aap key baad ki haalat mein kushadgi aur khushi mein aazamaye gaey to hum sabr na kar sakey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
2465,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jis ka maqsad aakhirat ki zindagi ho Allah Taala uskey dil mein beniyazi aur beparwaahi paida kar deta hai, aur usey dil jamai ata karta hai padhi. , aur duniya uskey paas zaleel ho kar aati hai aur jis ka maqsad talabe duniya ho, Allah Taala uski mohtaji uski dono aakhon key samney rakh deta hai aur uski dil jamai ko pareshan kar deta hai aur duniya uskey paas itni hi aati hai jo uskey liye muqaddar hai.''"
2466,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah taala farmata hai : ibne-Adam ! to meri ibadat key liye yaksu ho ja, main tera Sina beniyaazi aur beparwaahi sey bhar dunga, aur teri mohtaji door karunga, aur agar tu ney aisa na kiya to main tera dil mashghooliyat sey bhar dunga aur teri mohtaji door na karunga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
2467,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki wafat hui, us waqt hamarey paas thodi si jau thi, phir jitni muddat tak Allah Taala ney chaha hamney usi sey khaya , phir hamney laundi ko jau tolney key liye kaha, to usney tola , phir baqiya jau bhi jald hi khatam ho gaey, lekin agar hum usey chhod detey aur na tolte to is mein sey us sey ziyada muddat tak khatey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- yahan Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) key qol «شطر» ka maana qadrey aur thoda hai."
2468,"hamarey paas eik bareek parda tha jis par taswiren bani thin, parda merey darwazey par latak raha tha, jab usey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney dekha to farmaya : ''is ko yahan sey door kar do isliye ke ye mujhey duniyaa ki yad dilata hai.'' , Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) kehti hain : hamarey paas eik ro'ein daar purani chadar thi jis par resham key nishaanaat baney huye they aur usey hum audhte they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai."
2469,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas chamdey ka eik takiya ( bistar ( tha jis par aap aaram farmatey they is mein khajoor ki patli chhaal bhari hui thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai.
2470,"ney eik bakri zibeh ki, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney puchha ''is mein sey kuchh baqi hai?'' Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ney kaha : dasti key siwa aur kuch nahin baqi hai, aap ney farmaya : ''dasti key siwa sab kuchh baqi hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai."
2471,"hum aale Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ( aisey they ke eik eik mahina choolhaa nahin jalaatey they, hamara guzar basar sirf khajoor aur pani par hota tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai."
2472,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''mujhey Allah ki raah mein aisa daraya gaya ke is tarah kisi ko nahin daraya gaya aur Allah ki raah mein mujhey aisi takleefen pahunchaai gaee hain ke is tarah kisi ko nahin pahunchaai gaeen , mujh par musalsal tees din aur raat guzar jatey aur merey aur Bilal key liye koi khana nahin hota ke jisey koi jaan wala khaye siwaye thodi si chiz key jisey Bilal apni baghal mein chhupa letey they.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2ـ is hadees mein wo din murad hain ke jab aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ehale Makka sey bezar ho kar Makka sey nikal gaey they aur sath mein Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) they, unkey paas kuchh khana tha jisey wo baghal mein dabaaey huye they."
2473,"eik thandey din mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key ghar sey main nikla aur sath main eik badbudar chamdaa ley liya jis key baal jhadey huye they, phir beech sey mainey usey kaat kar apni gardan mein dal liya aur apni kamar ko khajoor ki shaakh sey baandh diya, mujhey bahut sakht bhook lagi hui thi, agar Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key ghar mein kuchh khana hota to main is mein sey zarur kha leta , chunanche main kuchh khaney ki talash mein nikla , raastey main eik Yahudi key paas sey guzra jo apney baagh mein charkhi sey pani dey raha tha, us ko mainey deewar ki eik surakh sey jhaankaa to usney kaha : Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) ! kya baat hai? kya to eik khajoor par eik dol pani kheencheyga? mainey kaha : haan , aur apna darwaza khol do taake main andar aa jaaun, usney darwaza khol diya aur main dakhil ho gaya, usney mujhey apna dol diya, phir jab bhi main eik dol pani nikalta to wo eik khajoor mujhey deta yahan tak ke jab meri mutthi bhar gaee to mainey uska dol chhod diya aur kaha ke itna merey liye kafi hai, chunanche mainey usey khaya aur do teen ghoont pani piya , phir main masjid mein aaya aur wahin Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko mojud paya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
2474,Sahaba ko eik martaba bhook lagi to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sab ko sirf eik eik khajoor di. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2475,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamein teen sau ki tadaad mein bheja , hum apna apna zaade-safar (safar ka khaana) uthaey huye they, hamara zaade safar khatam ho gaya nobat yahan tak pahunch gaee ke har aadmi key hissey mein sirf eik eik khajoor aati thi, un sey kaha gaya : abu-Adbullah ! eik khajoor sey aadmi ka kya hota hoga? jab wo bhi khatam ho gaee to hamein uski qadr malum hui, unhoney farmaya : hum samandar key kinarey pahunchey aakhir hamein eik machhli mili , jisey samandar ney bahar phenk diya tha, chunanche hum is mein sey atthaara din tak jis tarah chaha sair ho kar khatey rahey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees Jabir key wastey sey dusri sanadon sey bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai. 3- is hadees ko Malik bin Anas ney Wahab bin Kaisaan sey is sey ziyada mukammal aur lambi riwayat kiya hai."
2476,"hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath masjid mein bethey huye they ke Musab bin Umer padhi. aaye unkey badan par chamdey ki pewand lagi hui eik chadar thi, jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen dekha to unki us naaz aur nemat ko dekh kar roney lagey jis mein wo pehley they aur jis haalat mein in dino they, phir Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''kya haal hoga tumhara us waqt jabke tum mein sey eik shakhs eik jodey mein subah kerega to doosrey jodey mein Sham kerega aur uskey samney eik bartan khaney ka rakha jaeyga to doosra uthaya jaeyga, aur tum apney makaanon mein aisey hi parda dalo gey jaisa ke Kaabe par parda dala jata hai?'' ,Sahaba ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! kya hum us waqt aaj sey bahut achvhhey hongey aur ibadat key liye farigh hongey aur mehnat aur mashaqqat sey bach jaeyngey? to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''nahin , balke tum aaj key din un dino sey behtar ho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- Yazeed bin Ziyad sey murad Yazeed bin Ziyad bin Maisraa Madni hain, un sey Malik bin Anas aur deegar ehle-ilm ney riwayat ki hai aur (doosrey) Yazeed bin Ziyad Dimashqi wo hain jinhoney Zohri sey riwayat kiya hai aur un sey (yani Dimashqi sey) Wakee aur Marwan bin Muawiya ney riwayat kiya hai, aur (teesrey) Yazeed bin Abi Ziyad Koofi hain."
2477,"ehale Suffa musalmanon key mehman they, wo maal aur ehal aur ayaal waley na they, qism hai us mabood ki jis key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin, bhook ki shiddat sey main apna pet zamin par rakh deta tha aur bhook sey pet par pathar baandh leta tha, eik din main logon ki guzargaah par beth gaya, us taraf sey abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) guzrey to mainey un sey Quran Majeed ki eik aayat is wajeh sey poochhi taake wo mujhey apney sath ley jaeyn lekin wo chaley gaey aur mujhey apney sath nahin liya, phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) guzrey , un sey bhi mainey kitabullah ki eik aayat poochhi taake wo mujhey apney sath ley jaeyn magar wo bhi aagey badh gaey aur mujhey apney sath nahin ley gaey. phir Abul-Qaasim Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka guzar huwa to aap ney mujhey dekh kar muskuraayaa aur farmaya : ''Abu-Huraira ! ''main ney kaha : hazir hun Allah key Rasool ! aap ney farmaya : ''sath chalo'' aur aap chal padey, main bhi sath mein ho liya , aap apney ghar mein dakhil huye phir mainey bhi ijazat chahi , chunanche mujhey ijazat dey di gaee , wahan aap ney doodh ka eik piyala paya , daryaft farmaya : ''ye doodh kahan sey mila?'' arz kiya gaya : falan ney isey hadiya bheja hai, aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Abu-Huraira !'' mainey kaha : hazir hun, aap ney farmaya : ''jaao ehale Suffa ko bula laao.'' ,ye musalmanon key mehman they unka koi thikaana nahin tha, ghar-baar tha na koi maal, aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas jab koi sadqa aata tha to usey unkey paas bhej detey they, is mein sey aap kuchh nahin letey they, aur jab koi hadiya aata to unko bula bhejtey, is mein sey aap bhi kuchh ley letey, aur u ko bhi is mein shareek farmatey, lekin us zara sey doodh key liye aap ka mujhey bhejna nagawar guzra aur mainey (dil mein) kaha : ehale Suffa ka kya baneyga? aur main unhen bulaney jaaunga, phir aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam mujhey hi hukm dengey ke is piyaley mein jo kuchh hai unhen dun, mujhey yaqin hai ke is mein sey mujhey kuchh nahin milega , halanke mujhey ummid thi ke is mein sey mujhey itna zarur milega jo merey liye kafi ho jaeyga, lekin Allah aur uskey Rasool ki itaat key siwa koi chaara bhi na tha, chunanche main un sab ko bula laya , jab wo sab aap key paas aaye aur apni apni jagahon par beth gaey to aap ney farmaya : ''Abu-Huraira ! ye piyala un logon ko dey do.'' ,chunanche main wo piyala eik eik ko deney laga, jab eik shakhs pi kar sair ho jata to main doosrey shakhs ko deta yahan tak ke main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam tak pahunch gaya, sari qom sair ho chuki thi (ya sab log sair ho chukey they) phir aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney wo piyala ley kar usey apney haath par rakha phir apna sar uthaya aur muskura kar farmaya : ''Abu-Huraira ! ye doodh piyo'' , chunanche mainey piya. phir aap ney farmaya : isey piyo main peeta raha aur aap yehi farmatey rahey yahan tak ke mainey kaha is zaat ki qism jisney aap ko haq ley kar bheja hai ab main peeney ki gunjaaish nahin paata, phir aap ney piyala liya , Allah ki hamd aur sanaa bayan ki aur Bismillah keh kar doodh piya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2478,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas eik shakhs ney dakaar liya, to aap ney farmaya : ''tum apni dakaar hum sey door rakho isliye ke duniya mein sab sey ziyada pet bhar kar khaney wala qiyamat key din sab sey ziyada bhookaa rahega.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein abu-Juhaifa (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2479,"unhoney kaha : aey merey betey ! agar tum hamen us waqt dekhtey jab hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath they aur hamen barish nasib hoti thi to tum khayal kartey ke hamari boo bhaid ki boo jaisi hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih hai. 2- is hadees ka matlab ye hai ke Sahaba key kapdey oon key hotey they, jab is par barish ka pani padta to us sey bhaid ki jaisi boo aaney lagti thi."
2480,"Ibrahim Nakhai kehtey hain : ghar makaan sab ka sab, har imarat, baaise wabal hai, mainey kaha is makaan key barey mein aap ka kya khayal hai, jisey banaey baghair chaara nahin unhoney kaha : na is mein koi ajr hai aur na koi gunah."
2481,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo shakhs zeenat ka libas khalis Allah ki raza-mandi aur uski tawaazeh ki khatir chhod dey bawajud ye ke wo usey muyassar hai to Allah Taala aisey shakhs ko qiyamat key din tamam makhluq key samney bulaeyga taake wo ehale eman key libas mein sey jisey chahey pasand karey , aur pehney. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- « حلل الإيمان » sey jannat key wo libas murad hain jo ehale eman ko diye jaeyngey."
2482,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''nafqa (bharan poshan) sab ka sab Allah ki raah mein hai siwaye us nafqa key jo ghar bananey mein kharch hota hai kyonkey is mein koi khair nahin hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai.
2483,"hum Khubab (Raziallahu anhu) key paas iyaadat karney key liye aaye , unhoney apney badan mein saat dagh lagwaa rakhey they, unhoney kaha : yaqinan mera marz bahut lamba ho gaya hai, agar main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko ye farmatey na suna hota ke ''maut ki tamanna na karo'' ,to main zarur iski tamanna karta , aur aap ney farmaya : ''aadmi ko har kharch mein sawab milta hai siwaye mitti mein kharch karney key''  ,ya farmaya : ''ghar bananey mein.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2484,"eik saail (sawaali) ney aa kar ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey kuchh maanga to ibne-Abbas ney saail (sawaali) sey kaha : kya tum ye gawahi detey ho ke Allah Taala key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin hai? usney kaha : haan , aap ney kaha : kya tum ye gawahi detey ho ke Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Allah key Rasool hain? usney kaha : haan , aap ney kaha : kya tum Ramzan key rozey rakhtey ho? usney kaha : haan , aap ney kaha : tum ney sawal kiya aur saail ka haq hota hai, beshak hamarey ooper zaruri hai ke hum tumharey sath husne-suluk karen, chunanche unhoney usey eik kapda diya aur kaha : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko ye farmatey huye suna hai : ''jo koi musalman kisi musalman bhai ko koi kapda pehnaata hai to wo Allah ki aman mein us waqt tak rehta hai jab tak us kapdey ka eik tukda bhi is par baqi rehta hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai."
2485,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab Madina tashrif laye to log aap ki taraf daud padey , aur kehney lagey : Allah key Rasool aagey , Allah key Rasool aagey , Allah key Rasool aagey , chunanche main bhi logon key sath aaya taake aap ko dekhun , phir jab mainey aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka chehra Mubarak achchhi tarah dekha to pehchan gaya ke ye kisi jhootey ka chehra nahin ho sakta , aur sab sey pehli baat jo aap ney kahi wo ye thi ''logo ! salam phailao, khana khilaao aur raat mein jab log so rahey hon to namaz padho, tum log salamti key sath jannat mein dakhil ho'ogey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai."
2486,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''khana kha kar Allah ka shukar ada karney wala ( ajr aur sawab mein) sabr karney waley roze daar key barabar hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai.
2487,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab Madina tashrif laye to aap key paas muhajrin ney aa kar arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! jis qom key paas hum aaye hain un sey badh kar hamney koi qom aisi nahin dekhi jo apney maal bahut ziyada kharch karney wali hai aur thodey maal honey ki surat mein bhi dusron key sath gham khawaari karney wali hai. chunanche unhoney hum ko mehnat aur mashaqqat sey baaz rakha aur hum ko aaram aur rahat mein shareek kiya yahan tak ke hamein khof hai ke hamari sari nekiyon ka sawab kahin unhin ko na mil jaey? Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''baat aisi nahin hai jaisa tum ney samjha hai jab tak tum log Allah sey unkey liye duaaey khair kartey rahogey aur unka shukriya ada kartey rahogey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai.
2488,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''kya main tumhen aisey logon ki khabar na dun jo jahannam ki aag par ya jahannam ki aag un par haram hai? jahannam ki aag logon key qarib rehney waley , aasani karney waley , aur naram akhlaq waley par haram hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
2489,"mainey Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey puchha kya : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab apney ghar mein dakhil hotey they to kya kartey they? kaha : aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam apney ghar walon key kaam kaaj mein mashghool ho jatey they, phir jab namaz ka waqt ho jata to khadey hotey aur namaz padhney lagtey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2490,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key samney jab koi shakhs aata aur aap sey musaafa karta to aap apna haath uskey haath sey nahin nikaltey jab tak wo shakhs khud apna haath na nikal leta, aur aap apna rukh uski taraf sey nahin phertey, jab tak ke wo khud apna rukh na pher leta, aur aap ney apney kisi sathi key samney kabhi paaon nahin phelaey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai."
2491,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum sey agli ummaton mein sey eik shakhs eik joda pehan kar is mein itraataa huwa nikla chunanche Allah Taala ney zamin ko hukm diya aur zamin ney us ko mazbooti sey pakad liya , isliye wo qiyamat key din tak zamin mein dhanstaa chala ja raha hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai."
2492,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''mutakabbir (ghamand karney waley) logon ko qiyamat key din maidane hashr mein chhoti chhoti chewntiyon key maanind logon ki Suraton mein laya jaeyga, unhen har jagah zillat dhaanpey rahegi, phir wo jahannam key eik aisey qaid khaney ki taraf haankey jaeyngey jis ka naam « بولس » hai. is mein unhen bhadakti hui aag ublegi, wo is mein jahannamiyon key zakhmon ki peep piyengey jisey « طينة الخبال » kehtey hain, yani sadi hui badbudar keechad.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2493,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney ghussey par qabu paa liya us haal mein ke uskey kar guzarney par qadir tha, to qiyamat key roz Allah Taala usey tamam logon key samney bulaeyga aur ikhtiyar dega ke wo jannat ki hooron mein sey jisey chahey pasand kar ley.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
2494,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''teen khaslatein aisi hain ke ye jis key andar paai jaeyn to qiyamat key roz Allah apni rehmat key saye taley rakheyga, aur usey apni jannat mein dakhil kerega :(1) zaeefon key sath naram bartaao karey. (2) maa baap key sath shafqat aur mohabbat ka bartaao karey. (3) laundiyon aur ghulamon par ehsan kerey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
2495,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah taala farmata hai : aey merey bando ! tum sab gumrah ho, siwaye uskey jisey main hidayat dun, isliye tum sab mujh sey hidayat maango main tumhen hidayat dunga , aur tum sab key sab mohtaj ho siwaye uskey jisey main ghani (maaldaar) kar dun, isliye tum mujh hi sey maango main tumhen rizq dunga, aur tum sab gunehgar ho, siwaye uskey jisey main aafiyat dun to jisey ye malum hai ke main bakhshney par qadir hun phir wo mujh sey maghfirat chahta hai to main usey maaf kar deta hun, aur mujhey koi parwah nahin agar tumharey agley aur pichhley , tumharey zinde aur murdey aur tumharey khushk aur tar sab merey bandon mein sey sab sey ziyada muttaqi aur perhezgar bandey ki tarah ho jaeyn to bhi meri saltanat main eik machchhar key par barabar izafa na hoga, aur agar tumharey agley aur pichhley , tumharey zinde aur murdey aur tumharey khushk aur tar sab merey bandon mein sey sab sey ziyada dil ke sakht aur bad-bakht ki tarah ho jaeyn to bhi meri saltanat main eik machchhar key par barabar kami na hogi , aur agar tumharey agley aur pichhley , tumharey zinde aur murdey aur tumharey khushk aur tar sab eik hi zamin par jama ho jaeyn aur tum mein sey har insan mujh sey itna maangey jahan tak uski aarzuein pahunchein aur main tum mein sey har saail (sawaali) ko dey dun to bhi meri saltanat mein kuchh bhi farq waqey na hoga magar itna hi ke tum mein sey koi samandar key kinarey sey guzrey aur us main eik soi dubo kar nikal ley, aur aisa is wajeh sey hai ke main sakhi , buzurg hun, jo chahta hun karta hun, mera dena sirf keh dena , aur mera azab sirf keh dena hai, kisi chiz key liye jab main chahta hun to mera hukm yehi hai ke main kehta hun ''ho ja'' bas wo ho jati hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- baaz logon ney isi tarah is hadees ko ba-tareeq : (عن شهر بن حوشب an معدي كرب an أبي ذر an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) riwayat kiya hai."
2496,"mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey eik hadees suni hai agar mainey usey eik ya do baar suna hota yahan tak ke saat martaba guna to main usey tum sey bayan na karta , lekin mainey usey is sey ziyada martaba suna hai, aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam farma rahey they : ''bani Israel mein Kifl naami eik shakhs tha jo kisi gunah key karney sey perhez nahin karta tha, chunanche uskey paas eik aurat aai , usney isey saath (60) Dinar isliye diye ke wo us sey bad-kari kerega, lekin jab wo uskey aagey betha jaisa ke mard apni biwi key aagey bethta hai to wo kaanp uthi aur roney lagi, us shakhs ney puchha : tum kyon roti ho kya mainey tumharey sath zabardasti ki hai? wo boli : nahin, lekin aaj main wo kaam kar rahi hun jo mainey kabhi nahin kiya aur is kaam key karney par mujhey sakht zarurat ney majbur kiya hai, chunanche usney kaha : tum aisa ghalat kaam karney ja rahi hao jisey tum ney kabhi nahin kiya, isliye tum jaao , wo sab Dinar bhi tumharey liye hain, phir us shakhs ney kaha : Allah ki qism ! ab iskey baad main kabhi bhi Allah ki nafarmani nahin karunga , phir usi raat mein uska intiqal ho gaya, chunanche subah ko uskey darwazey par likha huwa tha ''beshak Allah Taala ney Kafl ko bakhsh diya.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- isey Sheban aur deegar logon ney Aamash sey isi tarah marfooan riwayat kiya hai, aur baaz logon ney isey Aamash sey ghair marfoo riwayat kiya hai, abu-Bakar bin Ayash ney is hadees ko Aamash sey riwayat kiya hai lekin is mein ghalati ki hai, aur « an Abdullah bin Abdullah an Saeed bin Juber an ibne-Umar » kaha hai jo ke ghair mehfooz hai."
2497,"hum sey Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney do hadisein bayan kin , eik apni taraf sey aur dusri Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki taraf sey (yani eik maqoof aur dusri marfoo) Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : momin apney gunah ko aisa dekhta hai goya wo pahad ki jad mein hai. darta hai ke is par wo gir na padey, aur faajir apney gunah ko eik makkhi key maanind dekhta hai jo uski naak par bethi hui hai, usney haath sey ishara kiya aur wo ud gaee."
2498,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''yaqeenan Allah tum mein sey eik shakhs ki tauba par us shakhs sey kahin ziyada khush hota hai jo kisi be-aabo-giyaah chatiyal maidan (registaan) mein hai aur uskey sath uski oontni hai jis par uska tosha , khana pani aur deegar zarooraton ki chiz rakhi hui hai, phir uski oontni kho jati hai aur wo usey dhoondney key liye nikal padta hai, yahan tak ke jab wo halakat key qarib pahunch jata hai to wo sochta hai : main usi jagah lot jaaun jahan sey meri oontni kho gaee thi, aur wahin mar jaaun chunanche wo lot kar usi jagah pahunchta hai, aur is par neend taari ho jati hai, phir jab bedaar hota hai to kya dekhta hai ke uski oontni uskey sar key paas mojud hai is par uska khana pani aur hajat ki chiz bhi mojud hai.''Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , Noman bin Bashir aur Anas bin Malik (Raziallauh anhum) ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey hadisein riwayat ki hain."
2499,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''sarey insan khatakar hain aur khata-kaaron mein sab sey behtar wo hain jo tauba karney waley hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- isey hum sirf Ali bin Musada hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain jisey wo Qatada sey riwayat kartey hain.
2500,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhta ho to usey chahiye ke wo apney mehman ki izzat karey, aur jo Allah aur youme aakhirat par eman rakhta ho to usey chahiye ke wo bhali baat kahey ya khamosh rahey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Aaisha , Anas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2501,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo khamosh raha usney najat paai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- isey hum sirf ibne-Lahiaa ki riwayat sey jantey hain.
2502,"mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key samney eik shakhs ki naqal ki to aap ney farmaya : ''mujhey ye pasand nahin ke main kisi insan ki naqal karun aur mujhey itna aur itna maal miley.'' mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! beshak Safiya eik aurat hain, aur apney haath sey is tarah ishara kiya, goya ye murad ley rahi thin ke Safiya pasta qad hain. aap ney farmaya : ''beshak tum ney apni baaton mein aisi baat Milaai hai ke agar isey samandar key pani mein mila diya jaey to uska rang badal jaey.''"
2503,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main ye nahin pasand karta ke main kisi insan ki naqal karun aur mujhey itna aur itna maal miley.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2504,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey puchha gaya ke musalmanon mein sab sey ziyada afzal kon hai? aap ney farmaya : ''jis ki zaban aur haath sey doosrey musalman mehfooz hon.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Abu-Musa ki riwayat sey is sanad sey sahih gharib hai.
2505,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney apney kisi deeni bhai ko kisi gunah par aar (sharm) dilaaya to uski maut nahin hogi yahan tak ke us sey wo gunah sadir ho jaaey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- iski sanad muttasil nahin hai, aur Khalid bin Maadaan ki mulaqat Muaz bin Jabal sey Sabit nahin hai, Khalid bin Maadaan sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke unhoney sattar Sahaba sey mulaqat ki hai, aur Muaz bin Jabal ki wafat umr bin Khattab ki khilaafat mein hui, aur Khalid bin Maadaan ney Muaz key kaee shagirdon key wastey sey Muaz sey kaee hadisein riwayat ki hai. 3- Ahmed bin Munee ney kaha : is sey wo gunah murad hai jis sey wo shakhs tauba kar chuka ho."
2506,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''apney bhai key sath dushmani na karo, ho sakta hai ke Allah Taala is par reham karey aur tumhen aazmaaish mein dal dey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- Makhool ka samaa (sun'na), Waasila Isqaa', Anas bin Malik aur Abu Hind Daari sey Sabit hai, aur ye bhi kaha jata hai ke unka samaa (sun'na), in teeno Sahaba key ilawa kisi sey Sabit nahin hai. 3- ye Makhool Shaami hain unki kunniyat Abu-Adbullah hai, ye eik ghulam they baad mein unhen azad kar diya gaya tha. 4- aur eik Makhool Azdi Basraa bhi hain unka samaa (sun'na), Abdullah bin umr sey Sabit hai un sey Imaara bin Azan riwayat kartey hain. is sanad sey Makhool Shaami key barey mein marvi hai ke jab un sey koi masla puchha jata to wo «ندانم» (main nahin janta) kehtey they."
2507,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo musalman logon sey mail jol rakhta hai aur un sey pahunchney wali takleefon ko bardasht karta hai wo us musalman sey behtar hai jo na logon sey mel-jol rakhta hai aur na hi unki takleefon ko bardasht karta hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ibne-Abi Adi ney kaha : Shoba ka khayal hai ke Sheikh Sahabi (buzurg Sahabi) sey murad ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma hain.
2508,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aapsi phoot aur bughz aur adawat ki burai sey ijtinab (bacha) karo kyonkey ye (deen ko) moondney wali hai, aapsi phoot ki burai sey murad aapas ki adawat aur bughz aur hasad hai aur « الحالقة » moondney wali sey murad Deen ko moondney wali hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey sahih gharib hai."
2509,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''kya main tumhen aisi chiz key barey mein na bata dun jo darje mein salaat (namaz) , saum (roze) aur sadqe sey bhi afzal hai, Sahaba ney arz kiya : kyon nahin? zarur bataiye'' , aap ney farmaya : ''wo aapas mein mel-jol kara dena hai padhi. isliye ke aapas ki phoot Deen ko moondney wali hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai. Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi hai ke aap ney farmaya : ''yehi chiz moondney wali hai. main ye nahin keh raha hun ke sar ka baal moondney wali hai balke Deen ko moondney wali hai.''"
2510,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tumharey andar agli Ummaton ka eik marz ghus aaya hai aur ye hasad aur bughz ki bimari hai, ye moondney wali hai, main ye nahin kehta ke sar ka baal moondney wali hai balke Deen moondney wali hai, qism hai us zaat ki jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! tum log jannat mein nahin dakhil ho'o-gey jab tak ke eman na ley aao, aur momin nahin ho saktey yahan tak ke aapas mein mohabbat na karney lago, aur kya main tumhen aisi baat na bata dun jis sey tumharey darmiyan mohabbat qaaim ho : tum salam ko aapas mein phailao.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Yahya bin Abi Kasir sey is hadees key riwayat karney mein ehle-ilm ka ikhtilaf hai, baaz logon ney ye hadees : (عن يحيى بن أبي كثير an يعيش بن الوليد an مولى الزبير an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) ki sanad sey riwayat ki hai in logon ney is mein Zuber key waste ka zikr nahin kiya."
2511,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''bagawat aur qata' rehmi sey badh kar koi gunah aisa nahin hai jiska murtakib (mujrim) ziyada laaiq hai ke us ko Allah ki janib sey duniya mein bhi jald saza di jaey aur aakhirat key liye bhi usey baqi rakha jaey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2512,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : ''do khaslatein aisi hain ke jis shakhs key andar wo mojud hongi usey Allah Taala sabir aur shakir likheyga aur jis key andar wo mojud na hongi usey Allah Taala sabir aur shakir nahin likheyga, pehli khaslat ye hai ke jis shakhs ney Deen key aetbar sey apney sey ziyada Deen par amal karney waley ko dekha aur uski perwi ki aur duniya key aetbar sey apney sey kam haisiyat waley ko dekha phir us Fazal aur ehsan ka shukar ada kiya jo Allah ney is par kiya hai to Allah Taala usey sabir aur shakir likheyga. aur dusri khaslat ye hai ke jisney Deen key aetbar sey apney sey kam aur duniya key aetbar sey apney sey ziyada par nazar ki phir jis sey wo mehroom reh gaya hai is par usney afsos kiya, to Allah Taala usey sabir aur shakir nahin likheyga.''"
2513,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''un logon ki taraf dekho jo duniyaawi aetbar sey tum sey kam tar hon aur un logon ki taraf na dekho jo tum sey ooper hon , is tarah ziyada laaiq hai ke tum Allah ki un nematon ki na-qadri na karo, jo uski taraf sey tum par hui hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai."
2514,"main Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key paas sey rotey huye guzra to unhoney kaha : Hanzala ! tumhen kya ho gaya hai? mainey kaha : Abu-Bakar ! Hanzala to munafiq ho gaya hai) baat ye hai) ke jab hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas hotey hain, aur aap hamein jahannam aur jannat ki yad is tarah dilaatey hain goya hum usey apni aakhon sey dekh rahey hain, lekin jab hum duniyaawi karobar aur apney bachon mein wapis chaley aatey hain to us nasihat mein sey bahut kuchh bhool jatey hain, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Allah ki qism ! hamara bhi yehi haal hai. chalo hamarey sath Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas , chunanche hum dono chal padey, phir jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey dekha to farmaya : ''Hanzala ! tumhen kya ho gaya hai?'' mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! Hanzala munafiq ho gaya hai, jab hum aap key paas hotey hain aur aap hamein jahannam aur jannat ki yad is tarah dilaatey hain to wo hamari aakhon key samney hain, lekin jab hum duniyaawi karobar aur apney baal bachchon mein wapis lot jatey hain to bahut si baaten bhool jatey hain. Hanzala kehtey hain : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''agar tum hamesha isi keyfiyat mein raho jis kaifiyat mein merey paas hotey ho to yaqin jano ke farishtey tumhari majlison mein , tumharey raaston mein aur tumharey bistaron par tum sey musaafa karen  lekin aey Hanzala ! waqt waqt ki baat hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2515,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''koi shakhs momin kamil nahin ho sakta yahan tak ke wo apney bhai key liye wohi pasand karey jo apni zaat key liye pasand karta hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai.
2516,"main eik din Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath sawari par peechhey tha, aap ney farmaya : ''aey ladkey ! beshak main tumhen chand aham baaten batla raha hun : tum Allah key ehkam ki hifazat karo, wo tumhari hifazat farmaeyga, to Allah key huquq ka khayal rakho usey tum apney samney paaogey, jab tum koi chiz maango to sirf Allah sey maango, jab tum madad chaho to sirf Allah sey madad talab karo, aur ye baat jaan lo ke agar sari ummat bhi jama ho kar tumhen kuchh nafa pahunchana chahey to wo tumhen is sey ziyada kuchh bhi nafa nahin pahuncha sakti jo Allah ney tumharey liye likh diya hai, aur agar wo tumhen kuchh nuqsan pahunchaney key liye jama ho jaey to us sey ziyada kuch nuqsan nahin pahuncha sakti jo Allah ney tumharey liye likh diya hai, qalam utha liye gaey aur) taqdir key ( sahifey khushk ho gaey hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2517,"eik shakhs ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! kya main oont ko pehley baandh dun phir Allah par tawakkul karun ya chhod dun phir tawakkul karun? aap ney farmaya : ''usey baandh do, phir tawakkul karo.'' Amr bin Ali Al Falas kehtey hain : Yahya bin Saeed Al Qattan ney kaha ke hamarey nazdik ye hadees munkir hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Anas ki riwayat sey gharib hai, isey hum sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- isi tarah sey ye hadees Amr bin Umayya Zamri key wastey sey bhi Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
2518,"mainey Hasan bin Ali Raziallahu anhuma sey puchha : aap ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey kiya chiz yad ki hai? unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka ye farman yad kiya hai ke'' us chiz ko chhod do jo tumhen shak mein daley aur usey ikhtiyar karo jo tumhen shak mein na dale , sachchai dil ko mutmain karti hai, aur jhoot dil ko be-qarar karta aur shak mein mubtala karta hai'' padhi. , aur is hadees main eik qissa bhi hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Abul Horaa Sa'di ka naam Rabeea bin Sheban hai."
2519,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key samney eik aisey shakhs ka zikr kiya gaya jo ibadat aur riyaazat mein mash'hoor tha aur eik doosrey shakhs ka zikr kiya gaya jo darne aur perhezgari mein mashhoor tha, to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''koi bhi ibadat darne aur perhezgari key barabar nahin ho sakti.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, isey hum sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
2520,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo shakhs halal khaye, sunnat par amal karey aur log uskey shar sey mehfooz hon, wo jannat mein dakhil hoga.''  eik shakhs ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! aisey log to us zamaney mein bahut paey jatey hain?'' , aap ney farmaya : ''aisay log merey baad key zamanon mein bhi hongey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- hum is hadees ko Israel ki riwayat sey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
2521,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney Allah ki raza key liye diya aur Allah ki raza key liye roka aur jisney Allah ki raza key liye mohabbat ki, aur Allah ki raza key liye adawat aur dushmani ki aur Allah ki raza key liye nikah kiya to yaqinan uska eman mukammal ho gaya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees munkir hai."
2522,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jannat mein jo pehla giroh dakhil hoga unkey chehrey chaudahween raat key chaand ki surat hongey aur doosrey giroh key chehrey us behtar roshan aur chamakdaar sitarey ki tarah hongey jo aasman mein hai, un mein sey har shakhs ko do do biwiyan milengi, har biwi key badan par libas key sattar jodey hongey, phir bhi uski pindli ka goodaa bahar sey (gosht key peechhey sey) dikhai dega.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
